.\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 641, \"end\": 651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.6369090228449702, \"rank\": 0.570080977084044, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}, {\"begin\": 706, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.092124517512092e-13, \"text\": \"YouTube\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"a pattern\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"umbrage-seeking\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"the familiar follow-through\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"such provocations\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"SomeU.S.\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Christiansin particular have come to seem almost gleeful when such opportunities for cultural warriorism land in their laps-just as some snarky secularists delight in the all-too-easy goading of their Christian neighbors.\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 1056, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1036, \"end\": 1045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.8919551078153878, \"rank\": 0.12113265705613734, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cultural warriorism land\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"their laps\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"some snarky\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"delight\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-too-easy goading\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is asmall ironythat Thomas Jolly, the aptly named French cultural curator who put the scene on the Seine together, is at least partly able to indulge in his celebration of diversity (absent religious diversity of course) because generations agoEuropeans compelled by their Christian understanding of human dignityand solidarity baked that liberty into the founding principles of the European community.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1081, \"end\": 1087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9929749104385183, \"rank\": 0.0070458837725346475, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\"}, {\"begin\": 1111, \"end\": 1117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9960159236078272, \"rank\": 0.003808729600295113, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1160, \"end\": 1165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999871456567, \"rank\": 1.1215699186030431e-08, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 1334, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.8919551078153878, \"rank\": 0.12113265705613734, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1152}, {\"ngram\": \"his celebration\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1229}, {\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"absent religious diversity\", \"from\":